snippet.textDisplay: Coke Studio, thank you for an absolutely outstanding season!! There have been so many musical gems which have given me hours of great listening pleasure and will do so for a long time to come. You've made me laugh, dance, belt my heart out and brought me to tears. A standing ovation for all our fabulously talented artists and musicians. You make us beam with pride! <3 We love you so much! And a special pat on the back for Strings. The wait for next season is gonna be rough.
